<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Lupa Password - Qurban Manager</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Open+Sans:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="src/style.css">
</head>
<body class="login-body">
    <div class="login-container">
        <div class="login-card" style="text-align: center;">
            <div class="login-header">
                <h2>Lupa Password?</h2>
                <p>Ketikkan No WhatsApp / Email Anda yang terdaftar. Permintaan Reset Password akan kami proses.</p>
            </div>
            <form id="fwForm" class="login-form">
                <div class="input-group" style="text-align: left;">
                    <label for="kontak">Email / WA Akun Anda</label>
                    <input type="text" id="kontak" required>
                </div>